---
import Main from '../layouts/Main.astro';
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";

const hero = {
    head: "About Us",
    description: "Get to know me more alittle bit better."
}
---

<Main head={hero.head} description={hero.description}>
        <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Welcome to The Gallery! We are passionate about curating and showcasing beautiful art pieces from around the world. Our mission is to connect artists with art enthusiasts and provide a platform for creativity to flourish.</p>
            <p>Founded in 2023, The Gallery has quickly become a hub for art lovers, offering a diverse collection of paintings, sculptures, and digital art. We believe that art has the power to inspire, provoke thought, and bring joy to people's lives.</p>
            <p>Our team is dedicated to providing exceptional service and ensuring that every visitor has a memorable experience. Whether you're an artist looking to showcase your work or an art enthusiast seeking your next masterpiece, we invite you to explore The Gallery and discover the beauty of art.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our journey!</p>
        </div>
        </section>
</Main>